snippet.title: Action 4 Assange
snippet.description:
Action4Assange is a decentralized activist network working to promote the cause of #FreeSpeech and #FreeAssange and #FreeChelsea. We are not a legal entity and accept no donations and do not monetize content. We are a group of freely associating individuals expressing our freedom of speech/press

PLEASE DONATE TO WIKILEAKS, CHELSEA MANNING, OR THE COURAGE FOUNDATION
https://actionnetwork.org/fundraising...
https://couragefound.org/donate/
https://shop.wikileaks.org/donate

All opinions expressed are simply those of the person saying them. We do our best to report accurate and up to date information in this current culture of censorship and propaganda. If any information presented is inaccurate or misleading it is unintentional and corrections will be issued promptly at the beginning of each stream.

Found Us? Follow Us, Like and Subscribe!
https://www.twitter.com/action_4assange

Encrypted Inbox; ActionForAssange@protonmail.com
